          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-344-174F-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-344-174F-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-344-174F-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-1" n="1">When first the Squire and Tinker <hi rend="large-writing">Wood</hi></l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-2" n="2">Gravely consulting <hi rend="large-writing">Irelands</hi> good,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-3" n="3">Together mingled in a Mass</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-4" n="4">Smiths dust with Copper, Lead, &amp; Brass,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-5" n="5">The mixture thus by Chymick Art</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-6" n="6">United close in ev'ry part,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-7" n="7">In fillets rolld or cutt in peices</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-8" n="8">Appeard like one continu'd Species,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-9" n="9">And by the framing Engine struck</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-10" n="10">On all the same impression took;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-11" n="11">So to confound this hated Coyn</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-12" n="12">All partys and Religions joyn,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-13" n="13">Whigs, Torys, Trimmers, Hanoverians,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-14" n="14">Quakers, Conformists, Presbyterians,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-15" n="15">Scotch, Irish, English, French Unite</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-16" n="16">With equal Int'rest, equal Spight,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-17" n="17">Together mingled in a lump</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-18" n="18">Do all in our Opinion Jump,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-19" n="19">And every one begins to find</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-20" n="20">The same impression on his mind.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-21" n="21">A strange Event! whom Gold invites</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-22" n="22">To Warr and Bloodshed, Brass unites;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-23" n="23">So Goldsmiths say the coarsest stuff</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-24" n="24">Will serve for Sodder well enough.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-25" n="25">So by the Kettles loud alarm</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-26" n="26">The Bees are gatherd to a storm;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-27" n="27">So by the brazen Trumpets bluster</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-28" n="28">Troops of all Tongues &amp; Nations Muster;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-29" n="29">And So the harp of Ireland brings</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-30" n="30">Whole Crowds about its brazen strings.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-31" n="31">There is a chain lett down from Jove,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-32" n="32">But fasten'd to his Throne above,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-33" n="33">So strong, that from the lower end</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-34" n="34">(They say) all human things depend;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-35" n="35">This Chain, as ancient Poets hold,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-36" n="36">When Jove was young was made of Gold;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-37" n="37">Prometheus once this Chain purloynd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-38" n="38">Dissolv'd and into money coynd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-39" n="39">Then Whips me on a Chain of brass;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-40" n="40">(Venus was brib'd to lett it pass)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-41" n="41">Now while this brazen Chain prevaild</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-42" n="42">Jove saw that all Devotion fail'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-43" n="43">No Temple to his Godship raisd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-44" n="44">No Sacrifice on Altars blazd;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-45" n="45">In short, such dire confusion followd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-46" n="46">Earth must have been in Chaos swallowd;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-47" n="47">Jove stood amaz'd, and looking round,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-48" n="48">With much ado the Cheat he found,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-49" n="49">'Twas plain, he could no longer hold,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-50" n="50">The World in any Chain, but Gold;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-51" n="51">And to the God of wealth his Brother</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-52" n="52">Sent Mercury to gett another:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-53" n="53">Prometheus on a Rack is layd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-54" n="54">Ty'd with the Chain himself had made,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-55" n="55">On Icy Caucasus to shiver,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-56" n="56">Whilst Vultures eat his growing Liver.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-57" n="57">Ye pow'rs of Grubstreet make me able</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-58" n="58">Discreetly to apply this Fable;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-59" n="59">Say── Who is to be understood</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-60" n="60">By that old Theif Prometheus?── <hi rend="large-writing">Wood</hi>.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-61" n="61">For Jove, it is not hard to guess him,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-62" n="62">I mean His Maj──── God bless him;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-63" n="63">This Theif the Blacksmith was so bold,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-64" n="64">He strove to steal that Chain of Gold,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-65" n="65">Which links the Subject to the King,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-66" n="66">And change it for a brazen string;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-67" n="67">But sure, if nothing else must pass</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-68" n="68">Between the K── and Us, but Brass,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-69" n="69">Altho' the Chain will never crack,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-70" n="70">Yet Our Devotion may grow slack.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-71" n="71">But Jove will soon convert, I hope,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-72" n="72">This brazen Chain into a Rope,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-73" n="73">With which Prometheus shall be ty'd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-74" n="74">And high in Air forever ride:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-75" n="75">Where if We find his Liver grows,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-344-174F-line-76" n="76">Instead of Vultures We have Crows.</l>
          </lg>
